2/25/12 Alabama State

We had a huge day in Alabama, thank you everyone for turning out and supporting this event. This was a Record Breaker in itself. Biggest Alabama State meet to this date yet. Thank you Lifters and everyone that attended to support the lifters. We can't do it without you guys.  Also want to take a minute to thank Joe Ladnier, Wade Johnson, Amy Muynsterman for a fine job Judging, My wife Victoria and Heather for the great job on the score table and all you loader/Spotters. I appreciate everything all you guys do.
